Rogue Practice Doc

Each guild level, you will receive new skills. Not all skills
will be designed for your Rogue Cabal. You can still practice
any skill to the max allowed for your Cabal. You can practice
a skill anywhere by typing "practice <skill>" or "pra <skill>".
Also, skills have a chance to improve as you use them, so
you can conceivably max out all skills given time.
Since it is by using your skills, and gaining experience that
you advance, you can "practice level" when you have gained
enough training to increase your guild level.
